{"tid":1203212,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"聽朝出 今晚都要出","createTime":"2019-06-11T11:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T14:28:14.000Z","uid":200042,"like":68,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"7718a308faeb675c1342fad1f9a50edd0c9b79bf","tid":1203212,"uid":200042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:52:59.000Z","msg":"我知大家都有分析今晚出定聽朝好啲<br />\n但其實大家今晚去打頭炮好重要 就算唔打 去坐都會有壓力 可以引起注意 聽朝更多人去<br />\n<br />\n如果不斷講聽朝 今晚已下定決心去既人會失左人數優勢 所以大家請停一停諗一諗 不斷分化無好處 <br />\n<br />\n加上如果所有人一次過聽朝黎 人多又係混亂<br />\n所以今晚想去既 團結一齊去<br />\n聽朝想抖耐啲 你地聽朝分批去又得 <br />\n最重要有接力優勢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">坐埋一條船唔好分化</span>"},{"pid":"bb3b8495d006a78dc30cb69d1e360501bc04ead2","tid":1203212,"uid":200042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:53:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e579b143c71e95aacbe8058e49d1ef16744994","tid":1203212,"uid":200042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:54:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4140ac9b14139c23b85809449c364cc049d95d2","tid":1203212,"uid":200042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:55:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53aed70a5fa4068e67ffd6b0eaf017ef58a334b3","tid":1203212,"uid":49275,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:56:25.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n同意樓豬做法<br />\n今晚嘅巴打絕對要小心"},{"pid":"ddcd8157ff9862d693a46ed816f9d4973b5a1a9d","tid":1203212,"uid":200042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:01:14.000Z","msg":"真心㗎我 大家真係留意下 今晚去既ching無人幫就冚家剷<br />\n聽朝一人多又易亂"},{"pid":"25c6f2d0d29cc807b3254dccc777343148a4ccc1","tid":1203212,"uid":200042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:02:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6edd1bd6a5381b107cd98986fe8e060ab33a6823","tid":1203212,"uid":151429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:04:30.000Z","msg":"派完傳單即到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20fbdaff3411b0ed25f4ac59bb44f2505d379f85","tid":1203212,"uid":151429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:05:19.000Z","msg":"Btw大家小心唔好喺金鐘站出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed6802bc00ea023b3b3ad5ab5e71d12a904a6e78","tid":1203212,"uid":20809,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:08:30.000Z","msg":"我就今晚去，聽朝去根本就去唔到，黑警一定封晒路，迫到入去都開完會<br />\n<br />\n講咩今晚落雨仲on9,聽朝唔會落？<br />\n怕體力不支就返去訓教，唔好叫人聽朝<br />\n<br />\n總之今晚就包圍立法會，聽朝開唔到會"},{"pid":"b7546523b36cd2f10845ebdcc4b1f8ceff204769","tid":1203212,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:09:28.000Z","msg":"今晚出嘅，點都唔可以俾人捉到"},{"pid":"7ec7523561cb024c9a7a884941fe752162ccda0a","tid":1203212,"uid":200042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:13:24.000Z","msg":"大家都記得6/9啦 人多警犬封路咪又係迫 真係迫住又哂時間"},{"pid":"2a336a4d52e27b64565cdb7428233ec2cb097407","tid":1203212,"uid":15245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:15:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f527e8f5bd923e4c7979fec4a91ceea8f1a54a1f","tid":1203212,"uid":54303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:15:42.000Z","msg":"和理非幾時出都得 消耗下警力都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n勇武就只能祝你地好運"},{"pid":"e234b1de78e751cd8d0c4066830990113266c572","tid":1203212,"uid":200100,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:15:59.000Z","msg":"Pish 今晚唔去 唔知聽朝仲去唔去到 但最重要嘅就係今